        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2a0007-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_013-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T18:02:27.984+09:00">investigate the (texts of the) laws and regulations</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_017-114a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T18:06:38.748+09:00">The "old pronouncements",</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_017-114a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T18:07:00.416+09:00">the laws and regulations of the former kings,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_017-114a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T18:07:19.254+09:00">King Wen applied these</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:46:36.102+09:00">Man resembles the form of Heaven and Earth</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:46:57.535+09:00">He cherishes a nature (containing) the Five Constant (Virtues).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:47:07.667+09:00">His hearing and sight are sharp and clear.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:47:33.662+09:00">He is the most spiritually endowed of (all) living beings.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:48:05.124+09:00">His claws and teeth being insufficient to provide him with what he likes and wants,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:48:17.886+09:00">his rushing and running being insufficient to avoid danger,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:48:29.341+09:00">being without fur or feathers to keep off cold and heat,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:48:42.854+09:00">he effectively makes use of things in order to serve as nourishment;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:49:13.26+09:00">relying on his intelligence, he does not trust in (brute) strength.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:49:24.132+09:00">That is the reason why he is the noblest.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:49:52.716+09:00">However, if he had no sense of Goodness and of Love,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:52:03.397+09:00">unable to form groups, he would not be able to overcome the (living) things,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:52:03.979+09:00">his food would be insufficient.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:52:34.445+09:00">When groups have been formed and there is not sufficient,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:52:42.301+09:00">the spirit of contention will arise.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:53:20.19+09:00">The sages of antiquyity in a lofty manner having been the first to practise the virtues of respectful deference and universal love,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:53:35.659+09:00">the multitude rejoicing in their hearts followed after them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:54:03.089+09:00">Following after them they formed groups,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:54:23.593+09:00">and these (sages) were (their) rulers.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:54:38.273+09:00">They turned to them and went up to them</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:54:52.699+09:00">and these were their kings.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:55:00.548+09:00">The Hong Fan says:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:55:20.341+09:00">The Son of Heaven acts as the father and mother of the people;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:55:54.019+09:00">he is the king of all-under-Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:56:08.628+09:00">The sages adopting this example in order to rectify the names</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:56:29.289+09:00">said that the ruler was the father and mother (of the people)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:57:09.529+09:00">making it clear that Goodness and Love, together withVirtue and Deference,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:57:17.566+09:00">are the basis of true kingship.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:57:48.226+09:00">Love must be accompanied by respect, and so it is not corrupted;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:59:12.8+09:00">virtue needs to inspire awe and so it will last long.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T04:59:58.04+09:00">Therefore they instituted the Rules of Ceremonious Behaviour in order to give preeminence (the idea of) respect</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:00:17.861+09:00">and they made punishments to show forth their awe-inpsirign (might).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:00:40.002+09:00">Since the sages possessed enlightened and wise natures,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:00:54.299+09:00">they fully understsood the wishes of Heaven and Earth;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:01:27.359+09:00">(so) in making ritual rules, in providing instruction,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:01:50.157+09:00">in establishing laws and in instituting punishments,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:02:13.439+09:00">always  conforming to the feelings of the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:02:30.101+09:00">they took Heaven and Earth as their model and example..</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:02:56.617+09:00">Hence it is said that the former kings in establishing ritual rules</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:03:11.463+09:00">"took the brightness of Heaven as their model</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:03:46.584+09:00">and conformed to the nature of the Earth.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:04:52.142+09:00">(They made) punishments and penalties and (they had) awe-inspiring lawsuits,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:05:19.722+09:00">by means of which they emulated the killing and destruction of Heaven's thunder and lightning.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:05:46.079+09:00">(they were) kind and gentle, benevolent and harmonious,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:06:19.746+09:00">by means of which they imitated the productive and fostering action of Heaven".</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:07:05.265+09:00">The Book of Documents says: "Heaven advances those who possess ceremonious behaviour,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:07:27.605+09:00">Heaven punishes  those who commit crimes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:07:59.403+09:00">Therefore the sages according to Heaven's advancing instituted the Five (types of) Rules of Ceremonious Behaviour,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:08:26.923+09:00">and according to Heaven's punishing they made the Five Punishments.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:08:47.661+09:00">For the great punishments they used armour and arms;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:09:22.069+09:00">for the next (lower punishment) they used axe and battle axe;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:09:38.149+09:00">for medium punishment they used  knife and saw;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:09:55.737+09:00">for the next (lower punishment) they used drill and chisel,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:15:03.452+09:00">and for light punishments they used whip and rod.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:15:23.675+09:00">In serious cases (those executed) were laid out in the open field;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.57" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:15:38.499+09:00">in lesser cases they were brought to the marketplace or the court.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-1a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:16:01.613+09:00">The origin of (all) this is old.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:17:56.754+09:00">It dates from (the time of ) the Yellow Emperor when there was the battle of Zhuolu by which subdued the disaster of fire,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:18:22.724+09:00">whilst under Zhuanxu there was the campaign against Gonggong, by which he subdued the harm of the waters.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:18:40.645+09:00">The age of Tang and Yu was the acme of the best ordered government,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:19:02.87+09:00">was the acme of the best ordered government,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:19:19.624+09:00">but still they had to banish Gonggong,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:19:28.689+09:00">to expel Huantou,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:19:38.65+09:00">to make the Sanmiao skulk</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:19:44.637+09:00">and to kill Kun;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:20:01.837+09:00">then only did all-under-Heaven submit.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:21:12.265+09:00">(In the time of the) Xia (dynasty) there was the declaration about (the misdeeds of) Yu Hu (at) Gan.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:22:08.248+09:00">(and) the Yin and Zhou dynasties subdued all-under-Heaven by means of arms.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:22:28.336+09:00">When all-under-Heaven had been subdued,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:22:48.639+09:00">the shields and halberdswere collected and stored,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:23:43.538+09:00">whilst (the people) were taught by means of accomplished virtue</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:24:09.855+09:00">and yet (thee ancient rulers0 established the office of Master of the Horse</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:24:20.915+09:00">and instituted the host of the Six Armies.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:24:45.326+09:00">According to the well-field system they instituted the military tax.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:26:11.224+09:00">ten tong were one cheng;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:26:27.081+09:00">one cheng ws ten li square.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:26:36.282+09:00">Ten cheng were one zhong,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:26:43.514+09:00">ten zhong were one tong;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:27:04.865+09:00">one tong was one hundred li square.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:27:12.848+09:00">Ten tong were one feng</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T05:27:20.23+09:00">ten feng were one qi</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:11:49.198+09:00">the general taxes were to make food suffice,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:12:08.862+09:00">the miliary taxes were to make the arms suffice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:12:22.737+09:00">So four jing made up one yi</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:13:43.052+09:00">four yi made up one qiu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:13:43.301+09:00">one qiu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:13:43.639+09:00">being sixteen jing,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:13:54.191+09:00">(its military tax) consisting in one warhorse</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-2a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:13:55.52+09:00">and three head of cattle.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:17:39.295+09:00">The way of the Zhou (dynasty) declined</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:17:53.509+09:00">and the rules and regulations fell into decay.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:18:22.324+09:00">Coming now to the time when duke Huan of Qi appointed guan Zhong,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:18:43.946+09:00">the country became wealthy and the people were at ease.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:19:24.646+09:00">The duke asked him about the right way to exercise the hegemony and the use the army.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:19:33.119+09:00">Guan Zhong said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:20:10.636+09:00">"If you, oh Duke, desire to establish groups (of one hundred men) and squads of five men</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:20:25.874+09:00">and to make coats of armour and weapons,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:20:36.726+09:00">the large states will likewise make them</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:21:06.567+09:00">whilst the lesser states will set up (defensive) preparations,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:21:36.021+09:00">and then it will have become difficult thereby quickly to attain your purpose."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:22:10.437+09:00">Thereupon he created the internal administrations, entrusting  the military organisation to it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:22:26.171+09:00">So the geroups and squads were determined for the hamlets</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:22:53.584+09:00">whilst the military administration was complete on the borders.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:23:50.686+09:00">He linked together the platoons of ten and the squads of five</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:24:02.815+09:00">(so that) in staying and dwelling they shared each other's joys</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:24:17.08+09:00">and in life and death they shared each other's grief;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:24:27.967+09:00">fortune and misfortune they had in common.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:24:57.488+09:00">Therefore, when fighting at night they heard eah other's voices,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:25:19.862+09:00">and when fighting in the day-time they could see each other</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:25:44.35+09:00">(so that) in an emergency they were fully capable of dying for each other.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_015-3a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-02T07:26:07.279+09:00">When their training was completed</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T21:53:32.704+09:00">The road long with to guide the people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:16.111+09:00">The road long with to guide the people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:17.124+09:00">for ten years down to the present,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:16.902+09:00">yet to the countryside there has not been added any newly broken land,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:17.218+09:00">and [as soon as] one yearhs not a good harvest,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:17.35+09:00">the people have hungry looks.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:17.55+09:00">This [shows that] those who apply themselves. to [agriculture] are still too few,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:17.725+09:00">and that moreover the officials have not especially put their attention on it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:17.945+09:00">I have many times put forth edicts,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:18.148+09:00">and yearly have urged the people to plant and sow,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:18.366+09:00">but the results [of my action] have not yet appeared.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:18.841+09:00">This is [because] the officials have not been diligent in upholding my edicts</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:19.064+09:00">or [because] the officials have not been intelligent in urging the people [to agriculture].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:45.156+09:00">Forsooth, my farmers [have suffered] very bitterly</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:16.512+09:00">is [to make them] devote themselves to fundamentals.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:00:16.985+09:00">We Ourselves have led the world in agriculture</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:45.371+09:00">and yet the officials have perceived none of it;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:45.53+09:00">how then can [the officials effectively[ encourage [agriculture]?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-50a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:45.727+09:00">Let there be granted to the farmers this year half of the land tax and tax on produce.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:45.914+09:00">[The edict] also said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:46.617+09:00">are the most advantageous [persons] in the world.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:46.385+09:00">The Cultivators of the Fields</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:46.617+09:00">are the fundamental sources of life.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:47.093+09:00">Honest officials</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:46.087+09:00">"The Filially Pious and the Fraternally Respectful</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:46.733+09:00">The Sanlao</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:46.906+09:00">are the teachers of the people.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:47.316+09:00">are an example to the people.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:54.352+09:00">We greatly approve of the conduct of these few [kinds of] grandees.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:54.549+09:00">Now in prefectures of ten thousand families</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:54.633+09:00">it is said, 'There are none who [are able to] conform to [the Emperor's] order.'</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:54.799+09:00">How can people's natures be really [so inadequate]?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:54.978+09:00">This is because the way the officials have of recommending the capable is not adequate.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:54.738+09:00">Let Internuncios be sent to recompense and make grants: to the Sanlao and the Filially Pious, five pieces of silk per person;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:54.893+09:00">to the Fraternally Respectful and the Cultivators of the Fields, two pieces,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:55.087+09:00">to the honest officials of [the rank of] two thousand piculs and above for every hundred piculs three pieces,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:55.266+09:00">When [the Internuncio] arrives, [let him] ask the people if there is anything inconvenient or discontenting,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:55.465+09:00">and let him establish the regular number of Sanlao, Fillially Pious, Fraternally Respectful, and Cultivators of the Fields, in accordance with the number of households and people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_004-51a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-02-26T22:14:56.154+09:00">and order each to apply himself with all his mind in order to guid the people [aright]."</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
